  "description": "Oscar sleeping in a warm current. morph_morph at 0.2 — near the first oscillator pole, barely stirring. Slow drift (0.05) like the gentle pulse of gill filaments. Long attack and release hold the note like a held breath. Filter warm and soft, resonance minimal. An axolotl at rest is not absent — it is simply very, very present.",
